Paper: hep-th/0006061

Date: 2000-06-08

Title: A model for time-dependent cosmological constant

Comments: 5 pages, Revtex (multicol). Revised version to appear in Classical

and Quantum GravityJournal-ref: Class.Quant.Grav. 18 (2001) 1261-1268

We present a model for a spacetime dependent cosmological {\it constant}. Wemake a realization of this model based on a possible quantum aspects of theinitial stage of the universe and relate the cosmological constant with thechiral anomaly.